{"id": 412, "genre": 1001, "title": "出去聚会，你最讨厌什么样的人？", "description": "简直不能更讨厌。", "record_count": 11410, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194332WE5YkHzcI10V6dyv.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-07-03T12:00:43Z", "options": [{"id": 3177, "content": "乱... ...", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234708CxRhsyfdXj4tLmWi.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2933, "content": "带一桌子小孩", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 128617}, {"id": 2934, "content": "一直玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135652}, {"id": 2935, "content": "不停拍照不停装逼 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 128595}, {"id": 2936, "content": "选项好多都赞一遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 98295}, {"id": 2938, "content": "不搭理我的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124680}, {"id": 2940, "content": "满嘴义气逼喝酒  喝多还撒泼  低头手机党", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135747}, {"id": 2937, "content": "喝点酒就装逼削这个人干那个人的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2941, "content": "不好意思，我酒精过敏???", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135699}, {"id": 3130, "content": "挤得要死还把包放在座位上占一块地方，叫他就装傻?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137148}, {"id": 2825, "content": "挑食。你怎么不回家吃屎呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 141, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1091}, {"id": 2827, "content": "在饭桌上为了是中医粉还是中医黑吵翻天的", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114367}, {"id": 2830, "content": "明明大家都是学生，装得自己特别老练世故", "image": null, "praise_count": 393, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2846, "content": "装逼！", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2826, "content": "“我钱不够了能不能先借我点”然后就没有然后了", "image": null, "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 123244}, {"id": 2831, "content": "不停逼叨叨逼叨叨吹嘘自己女朋友的", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131290}, {"id": 2834, "content": "饭桌上无底线秀恩爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 123, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 2845, "content": "我还挺害怕聚会…的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112264}, {"id": 2832, "content": "明明不熟没什么话可说还说话都在酒里了的人(断句略难哈哈)", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 73617}, {"id": 4321, "content": "吝啬狗和嘚瑟狗…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145884}, {"id": 2816, "content": "迟到党，还有明明都约好了到日子却说不来了的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 610, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117258}, {"id": 2817, "content": "万事藏于心不表于情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134416}, {"id": 2799, "content": "喜欢劝酒，指着你的鼻子说“不喝就是看不起我”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1412, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2813, "content": "不太喜欢总是抱怨职场里的那些事的。听一两次还好，大家帮忙出谋划策一下。总是负能量满满，搜不鸟啊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 219, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 105432}, {"id": 2818, "content": "永远不买单的人和餐桌霸主！", "image": null, "praise_count": 345, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 58260}, {"id": 2815, "content": "刚坐下就说“我8点还有一个局”", "image": null, "praise_count": 435, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 103970}, {"id": 3072, "content": "默默无闻，只会玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136143}, {"id": 2894, "content": "非要把自己当做饭局的主角", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234827m8PMKoCHbz1tR9cF.jpg", "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135035}, {"id": 2896, "content": "到处逼逼 一个人喋喋不休", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135133}, {"id": 2897, "content": "明明约好了，约定时间一条短信过来说不来了，呵呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2898, "content": "大家一起的局，一言不发，或者偶尔敷衍一两句，特别沉浸在自己世界里的高冷星生物。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2905, "content": "永远在讲述她的情感血泪史，永远是被男人背叛抛弃的苦情戏女猪脚。我想说扒开伤口晒给别人看一千一万次有意思吗？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133206}, {"id": 2907, "content": "说好一起吃饭，来了又说减肥不吃，不吃这不吃那，不让别人好好吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135283}, {"id": 2908, "content": "说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135298}, {"id": 2913, "content": "不懂装懂 被别人戳穿还死不承认", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 132120}, {"id": 2909, "content": "装逼狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 116936}, {"id": 2910, "content": "一上来就问你做什么工作 赚多少", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 119650}, {"id": 2914, "content": "虚伪的，巴结上司的", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234800RLf7BYorA91KUizm.jpg", "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135372}, {"id": 2915, "content": "问你工作，问你生活，非要问个清楚，问完特扯的来句哥们没你这命啊。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135424}, {"id": 2872, "content": "有一种最恶心，，看着特别“诚信诚意”跟你喝酒 ，你不喝吧 他就不高兴了，说你不给面子，你忍着都喝了 他在那 叫好，这都没什么不对，事后他跟人说  那个傻逼 谁让喝酒他都喝， 真傻逼 。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2871, "content": "干什么 就是喝酒，，因为他们放下酒就什么都谈不了了。。。我真的看不上这种人，你不喝醉他觉得是在挑战他，觉得你心机重   各种灌你酒，，然后 喝完酒 就像傻逼一样 什么都哈哈哈，，我恨不得往他嘴里赛屎。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2875, "content": "总是说，这有什么好吃，那地方有什么好去，啥都没意思的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131970}, {"id": 3074, "content": "你说去干嘛，他都说随便，但是只要你说出一个主意，他都会找各种理由反对，但是问他主意时，他永远再说随便", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234709daim4cXZogYyrwvS.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136143}, {"id": 3018, "content": "不怕一直在说话的，就怕一直在说逻辑不通的话的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5}, {"id": 3019, "content": "装逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136278}, {"id": 3021, "content": "自大狂，那些以为自己是主角的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 132349}, {"id": 2801, "content": "饭量大，且付钱时永远没带钱 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 611, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2803, "content": "炫富狗——“我上次从阿尔及利亚度假回来买的XXX还挺好用的呢，只要9万。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 912, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2810, "content": "最怕傻逼爱得瑟", "image": null, "praise_count": 740, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 2812, "content": "真是日了狗了。是不是该打狂犬疫苗了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 121370}]}